## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-102"><xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestErrorEvent> Web 要求期間發生錯誤時引發。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-102">The <xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestErrorEvent> is raised if an error occurs during a Web request.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-103">您的應用程式應該使用這個事件來取得要求的相關資訊，所定義的<xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestInformation>和<xref:System.Web.Management.WebThreadInformation>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-103">Your application should use this event to obtain request-related information as defined by the <xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestInformation> and the <xref:System.Web.Management.WebThreadInformation> classes.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-104">在大部分情況下，您將使用標準 ASP.NET 健康監視類型並設定以控制其行為`healthMonitoring`組態區段。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-104">In most cases you will use the standard ASP.NET health monitoring types and control their behavior by setting the `healthMonitoring` configuration section.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-105">您也可以建立自訂型別下, 一個範例所示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-105">You can also create custom types, as shown in the next example.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-106">如果您建立自訂的事件類型，而且您需要新增您自己的資訊，請自訂<xref:System.Web.Management.WebBaseEvent.FormatCustomEventDetails%2A>方法，這會避免覆寫或竄改機密的系統資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-106">If you create your custom event type and you need to add your own information, customize the <xref:System.Web.Management.WebBaseEvent.FormatCustomEventDetails%2A> method, this will avoid overwriting or tampering with sensitive system information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
