 <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-107">下列程式碼範例有兩個部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-107">The following code example has two parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-108">第一個部分是組態檔可讓 ASP.NET 使用自訂事件的摘錄。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-108">The first part is an excerpt of a configuration file that enables ASP.NET to use a custom event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="efbf3-109">第二個部分示範如何衍生自<xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestErrorEvent>類別來建立自訂的事件。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="efbf3-109">The second part shows how to derive from the <xref:System.Web.Management.WebRequestErrorEvent> class to create the custom event.</span></span>  
  
```  
<healthMonitoring enabled="true" heartBeatInterval="0">  
  <eventMappings>  
    <add  name="SampleWebRequestErrorEvent" type="SamplesAspNet.SampleWebRequestErrorEvent,webrequesterrorevent,Version=1.0.1573.21654, Culture=neutral, PublicKeyToken=63ada862a6c5af13, processorArchitecture=MSIL"/>  
  </eventMappings>  
  
  <rules>  
    <add   
      name="Custom Web Request Error Events"  
      eventName="SampleWebRequestErrorEvent"   
      provider="EventLogProvider"    
      profile="Critical"/>  
  </rules>  
</healthMonitoring>  
```  
  
